Sat. Oct. 23

Fleetwood Maxx (Fleetwood Mac Tribute)
8:30 pm @ Lighthouse Bar at Twin River

Fleetwood Maxx performs all the classic Fleetwood Mac hits and has consistently sold out shows. Capturing the essence of the original performers, the band plays everything from the Rumours and Fleetwood Mac albums, and adds performances of duets originally performed with Tom Petty and Don Henley. Come relive the 70s and beyond with Fleetwood Maxx!
